<li>Priorities for the LIPs include: improving road safety, improving bus journey times and reliability, relieving traffic congestion and improving journey time reliability, improving the working of parking and loading arrangements, improving accessibility for all on the transport network, encouraging walking and cycling and bringing transport infrastructure into a good state of repair </li>
